Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.63,0:00:02.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:04.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time for Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:06.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gather all the shards\nof the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I'll destroy Naraku\nwith my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:12.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to Myoga, we narrowly\nescape death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:15.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we're following a new lead\ntowards a Sacred Jewel shard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:16.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:18.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is Kikyo here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:20.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku, Sango, Shippo and Kirara...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:21.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}travel back in time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:22.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To a Feudal Fairytale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:24.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.19,0:02:10.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To live is to die,\NTo die is to live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My name is Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:17.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A priestess unable\nto reach the sacred place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:20.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No... priestess is but\na label.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:24.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am actually a corpse\nwith a cursed existence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:29.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how much I desire\nto help others...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.45,0:02:33.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I live off the souls\nof dead persons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:40.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure is impure.\NImpure is pure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:46.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good is bad.\NBad is good... Or is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:51.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In the heart of man\nlie good and evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:54.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The two coexist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:57.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Men can become good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:02:59.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And they can become evil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:00.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:03.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That physician who calls\nhimself Suikotsu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is one of the dead like myself,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:10.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he looks after\norphaned children{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:13.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and gives medical attention\nto the villagers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:18.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems as though he hangs on to life\nthrough the Shikon Jewel shard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:23.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I can detect no cloudiness\nin its glow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:26.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only the heart of goodness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:28.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A pure spirit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:32.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is there truly such a person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shall watch the situation\na bit longer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:49.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:52.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll take over the guard.\NYou should rest, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:54.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:56.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've had enough sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:04:00.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, the Band of Seven won't\nattack anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:06.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,According to Koga,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:10.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he defeated the one named\NKyokotsu, of the Band of Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Sesshomaru defeated\NMukotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:17.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you beat Ginkotsu,\ndidn't you, Inuyusha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:28.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arghh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:42.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arghh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:53.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, three of the Band of Seven\nhave been beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:56.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's a huge blow to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:57.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:02.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why, before the Band of Seven\nregroup and attack again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:04.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to make the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First move?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:09.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What else? Hunt them down\nand get rid of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:14.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.\NThat's just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are lots of ways\nto find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They reek of dead bodies\nand graveyard soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:24.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And those wretches possess\NSacred Jewel shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:27.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will not forgive them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:29.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll find them without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:44.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:45.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I promise to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:48.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Doctor! It's too late\nfor that child!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:50.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kill her and escape from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:53.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's still hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:55.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The samurai are heading\nthis way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:57.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you don't make a run for it,\nyou'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:02.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Flee if you want!\NI'm going to save this child!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:13.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing, fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:15.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:19.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't you stop acting\nlike a saint already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:22.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The real you could care\nless about saving people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:27.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Deep inside, you want to hurt\npeople, to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:31.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not true!\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:33.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yo! We've come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:38.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez! Will you stop being\nsuch a pain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:39.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aghh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Idiot!\NYou can't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aghh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:49.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:54.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-It was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:03.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a horrible dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:06.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're awake already, Suikotsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:06.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:11.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... Good morning, Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:12.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:19.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looks like it'll be a\nfine day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:22.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I cannot understand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:25.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've kept a close watch\non this man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:28.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet I can feel no presence\nof evil about him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:32.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I see is the face of\na good doctor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:37.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So why has such a man\ngrounded his spirit in this world?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:41.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Over that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel a faint presence\nof a Sacred Jewel shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:45.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've found the Band of Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:48.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this Band of Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:58.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, there are more of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah. So what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:01.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:02.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:03.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:07.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:10.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just remembered\nsome business I must tend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:13.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll excuse myself now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:15.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:20.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What kind of business\ndoes he have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:22.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:27.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all due to Myoga that\nwe're alive today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:29.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:30.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:32.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:35.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you, Myoga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:37.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is Dr. Suikotsu away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, he went to pick\nmedicinal herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:43.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:45.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will tend to you\nin his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:48.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha,\nthere's something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:54.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:58.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Until now, the Sacred Jewel shards\npossessed by the Band of Seven were cloudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:00.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But this one's very clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:05.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then it doesn't belong to\nthe Band of Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:07.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu, I found some!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... this is green gentian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:15.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This one strengthens\nthe stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:18.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll pick these,\nthen go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:19.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:31.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're one of the Band of Seven,\naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:32.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:36.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu came to this village
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:40.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,shortly after the tombs of the\NBand of Seven broke apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:43.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tombs of the Band of Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:44.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On top of that, Dr. Suikotsu\nhad the same name
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:50.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,as one of the Band of Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:54.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So there was a panic among the villagers\nwho believed he was a specter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who had escaped from the tomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suikotsu is a specter\nof the Band of Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:02.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:05.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if the name is the same,\nhe is totally the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:11.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I saw the execution of the Band of Seven\nwith my very own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:14.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was long ago, but\NI remember it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:18.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It occurred fifteen years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:22.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Seven mercenaries who escaped\nfrom the east
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:26.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,committed countless atrocities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:30.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They fell into a trap set\nby the lord of the region
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and were executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suikotsu, one\nof the Band of Seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:40.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,was a mean one with\na diabolical expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:44.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But our Suikotsu is\ntotally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:47.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's a living saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:49.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:51.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The pain's all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:57.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are lots of effective\nmedicinal herbs around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:03.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please say hello to\NDr. Suikotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:05.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:07.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The presence of a shard...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:08.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:10.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's approaching.\NTwo of them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:12.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, three.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:15.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:19.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit acting dumb, Band of Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:20.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:21.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's some mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:25.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am a physician!\NI am not the Band of Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:27.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't try to deny it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:31.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your body emanates the smell\nof death and graveyard soil...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,just like the rest\nof the Band of Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:35.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:36.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:39.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll make you show your true colors!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:41.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't hurt the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:45.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you...!\NWhat're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:58.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Dr. Suikotsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:04.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry and run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:06.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! We won't go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:09.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't run and leave you behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:14.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The way it looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:18.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you're the bad guy attacking\na good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:20.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:25.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's too different from the Band of Seven\nwe've encountered so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:27.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! It's all a put on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:29.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The same trick Renkotsu used!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:34.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't be fooled a second time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:38.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Show your true self!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:43.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-The village!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:49.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Everyone will be-!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:54.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey wait!\NWe're not done here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:58.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arghh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'd better run, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:55.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So they're the Band of Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:56.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:00.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What on earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:02.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So this is where you've been!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:05.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Suikotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:10.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez! You caused so much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:11.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:17.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on, Suikotsu.\NWe came all the way to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:18.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:36.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Who are you?\NJust what are you anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:42.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe that he's lying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:45.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what is going on?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:03.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Full of holes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:07.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've never seen battles\nconducted like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:09.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's probably the work\nof the Band of Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sense a Sacred Jewel\nshard nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:13.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:16.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This place reeks with their smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:22.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:29.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:32.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you were in this region, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:33.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lady Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:38.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo... What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:40.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can talk later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:46.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You guys... You're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:48.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:51.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:54.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll take care of you all\nright now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:57.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You managed to stay alive...\nfor nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:01.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll pay you back, big time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.53,0:16:06.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If only they didn't possess\NSacred Jewel shards,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:08.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd suck them into\nmy Wind Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:10.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay back, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:14.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not fully recovered!\NYou can't handle them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:15.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave 'em to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, Jakotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take care of Suikotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:22.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:24.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the one for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They intend to kill me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll handle Inuyasha and his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aww, Renkotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:38.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You always keep me away\nfrom Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:39.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:42.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe you've taken a liking\nto Inuyasha, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:47.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you keep talking such nonsense,\NI'll pull out that tongue of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit babbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:51.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll take you all on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:54.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:03.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're such a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:06.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These flames aren't even hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:07.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:11.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:13.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A net of fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:16.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arghh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:24.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bringing along all\nthese humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:27.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, that's your weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:28.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:31.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:35.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:41.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,C'mon, Suikotsu.\NDon't be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:45.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are,\nbut you've come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:49.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So why don't you just kill only me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why attack the whole village?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:55.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna\nkeep this up, Suikotsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:58.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:03.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I'll really kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:08.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fire, Ginkotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:26.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:29.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jakotsu, shame on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fire, Ginkotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:43.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:44.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:48.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you don't pay attention,\nyour friends will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:13.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The souls are leaving me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:19.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:31.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kids, stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:33.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:35.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:37.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:45.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:50.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:03.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:08.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the hell's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't he part of the Band of Seven?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:13.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:16.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I... I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:19.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:20.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:21.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:33.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure is impure.\NImpure is pure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure is impure.\NImpure is pure.{\i0}\nWhat're you doing, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:35.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:35.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good is Bad.\NBad is good.{\i0}\nWhat're you doing, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:35.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good is Bad.\NBad is good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:38.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good is Bad.\NBad is good.{\i0}\nQuit acting like a saint!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:40.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good is Bad.\NBad is good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good is Bad.\NBad is good.{\i0}\nYour heart craves killing...\nkilling people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:43.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your heart craves killing...\nkilling people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:45.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To live is to die.\NTo die is to live.{\i0}\nYour heart craves killing...\nkilling people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:47.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To live is to die.\NTo die is to live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:50.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To live is to die.\NTo die is to live.{\i0}\NThe Sacred Jewel shard\Nhas turned black!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:50.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To live is to die.\NTo die is to live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:59.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure is impure.\NImpure is pure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:04.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good is evil.\NEvil is good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:06.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:09.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:13.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:17.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's finally awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:19.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:26.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:30.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, hurry and save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:31.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:36.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-reaver, Soul-stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:53.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:57.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm Suikotsu of the Band of Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:46.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.56,0:23:48.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's a totally different person\nfrom a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.23,0:23:51.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Suikotsu has two hearts\nwithin him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:53.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.20,0:23:56.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As I thought, you're just one of the\NBand of Seven, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.57,0:23:57.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.44,0:23:59.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is how you conduct\nclose-quarters combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.54,0:24:02.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suikotsu's true self is awakened\nand he begins his assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:04.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ginkotsu bares his claws\nagainst Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:09.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Hidden in the Mist: Onward to Mt. Hakurei!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.48,0:24:12.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo reveals the power\nof the sacred mountain!
